WEBVTT

00:00:01.740 --> 00:00:33.280
The signs we see are clear, the end of this world is near, but how have they known

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:56.560
the way to go without a chance, the truth we cannot hide, our fear we must set aside.

00:00:56.560 --> 00:01:32.230
Look to God, we'll make His message known, we know let's keep it and spread His glorious light.

00:01:32.230 --> 00:02:07.849
We know we can't hold, so let's hide.
